5|$|Reaction forces: A {{modified}} 16 Air Assault Brigade and an {{armoured division}} (3rd Division (United Kingdom) of three <b>armoured</b> <b>infantry</b> <b>brigades</b> (1st, 12th and 20th <b>Armoured</b> <b>Infantry</b> <b>Brigades).</b> In 2020, this division will reorganise and consist of two <b>armoured</b> <b>infantry</b> <b>brigades</b> and two strike brigades.|$|R
